Resource.Name: M-TX-01 | Embroidery machine
Resource.Description:
Location: Munich

Max. booking time: 4 h

Min. age: 16 years old


Course requirement:

TX-002 | Stickmaschine für Einsteiger


The embroidery machine is used for the creation of embroideries, i.e. the decoration on fabric by sewn-on or sewn-in threads. With this six-needle machine you can design patterns with up to six different colors.
